{
  "page": "Jaehaerys Targaryen",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Jaehaerys Targaryen</b> is the name of several members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a>. These include:\n</p>\n<ul><li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>, fourth Targaryen King on Iron Throne, third son of King Aenys Targaryen and Queen Alyssa Velaryon.</li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_Targaryen_(son_of_Aegon_II)\" title=\"Jaehaerys Targaryen (son of Aegon II)\">Jaehaerys Targaryen</a>, eldest son of King Aegon II Targaryen and Queen Helaena Targaryen, who died during the Dance of the Dragons.</li>\n<li>King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys II Targaryen\">Jaehaerys II Targaryen</a>, sixteenth Targaryen King on Iron Throne, second son of King Aegon V Targaryen and Queen Betha Blackwood.</li>\n<li>Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_Targaryen_(son_of_Aerys_II)\" title=\"Jaehaerys Targaryen (son of Aerys II)\">Jaehaerys Targaryen</a>, fourth son of King Aerys II Targaryen and Queen Rhaella Targaryen, who died young.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Feminine_equivalent\">Feminine equivalent</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jaehaerys_Targaryen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Feminine equivalent\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaera_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaera Targaryen\">Jaehaera Targaryen</a>, only daughter of King Aegon II Targaryen and Queen Helaena Targaryen, first queen of King Aegon III.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403092136\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visite